        <num>CCRP 214</num>
        <heading>214.  Arrest by private person; when lawful</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 214.  Arrest by private person; when lawful
A private person may make an arrest when the person arrested has committed a felony, whether in or out of his presence.</p>
        </content>
